<h1>Add member</h1>
<p>Use this window to add users and groups to <a href="../create-group">groups</a>.</p>

<p>Options:</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Search for a person or group to add</strong> - enter at least part of the user name or group name and select the user or group from the drop-down menu. This will add the selected user or group to the list below the input field. You can then select several users and groups at a time, or use the [...] button to select several items from the table at once (you can <a href="../../../../../alvao-asset-management/working-with-tables">customize the table contents</a>). Finally, confirm the selection with the <em>OK</em> button.</li>
</ul>

</asp:Content>
